What is the role of Kubelet?
Kubelet manages the containers that are scheduled to run on that node
it ensures that the containers are running and healthy
that the resources they need are available.

Kubelet communicates with kuberenets API server to get information about the containers that should be running on the node, and then start . 
and stopd the containers as needed to maintain the desired state.
it also monitiors the containers to ensure they running correctly and restrts them if necessary.
API SERVER NOTIFIES REPLICA SETS.
